      "side": 1,
      "message": "```suggestion\n  migration.\n  \n* [Change 523841](https://gerrit-review.googlesource.com/c/gerrit/+/523841):\n  Extend the Flows REST API with `ListActions`, so integrations can discover\n  which flow action types are currently offered by the configured flow service.\n\n* [Issue 483936085](https://issues.gerritcodereview.com/issues/483936085):\n  Add a new `aiReview` ref permission and expose `canAiReview` on `ChangeInfo`\n  so administrators can control access to AI review features per ref without\n  changing plugin configuration.\n\n* [Change 544621](https://gerrit-review.googlesource.com/c/gerrit/+/544621):\n  Add an `onBehalfOf` field to `ReviewerInput`, allowing privileged users to\n  add reviewers on behalf of another user while preserving the real actor in\n  reviewer update metadata.\n\n* [Change 559801](https://gerrit-review.googlesource.com/c/gerrit/+/559801):\n  Allow one plugin to replace a `DynamicItem` binding that was originally\n  provided by another plugin, enabling plugin-to-plugin API extension patterns\n  without core changes.\n```",
